    "short": "This sentence fits the gap because it connects logically to the surrounding text.",
    "full": "'When I get home, I can literally just kick them off and leav...' correctly completes the gap. It maintains the coherence and logical flow of the passage — connecting to the ideas before and after the gap. The other 4 options either break the logical flow, introduce unrelated ideas, or don't connect properly to the adjacent sentences.",
