    "full": "'I had a much-needed shower and unpacked my rucksack.' correctly completes the gap. It maintains the coherence and logical flow of the passage — connecting to the ideas before and after the gap. The other 4 options either break the logical flow, introduce unrelated ideas, or don't connect properly to the adjacent sentences.",
